OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774472757
OL,3,CWoman dies after a car crash in North
OL,4,CBelfast on Tuesday
OL,6,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fcan confirm that a woman aged in her
OL,8,F70s has sadly died following a single
OL,9,Fvehicle road traffic collision in
OL,10,Fnorth Belfast.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Stewart, from the
OL,13,FCollision Investigation Unit, said:
OL,14,F"Police received a report shortly
OL,15,Fafter 2.30pm yesterday, Tuesday 24th
OL,16,FMarch, of a collision involving a
OL,17,Ffemale pedestrian and a lorry in the
OL,18,FArdoyne Avenue area.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
