OL,3,CWoman dies after a car crash in North
OL,4,CBelfast on Tuesday
OL,6,F"Officers attended the scene, together
OL,7,Fwith colleagues from the emergency
OL,8,Fservices.
OL,10,F"Sadly, the woman was pronounced
OL,11,Fdeceased at the scene. "The area was
OL,12,Fclosed to traffic for a period of time
OL,13,Fbut has since re-opened.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@XOU
